lyrics.text: [Verse 1]
Fill out for me, I build a platform
You scrape later, me a changing arm
You watch the stock, then me a plot to storm
You drive autopilot, my mind transformed
Me no fear future, me a co-create
Give you the code, me walk through game
From nine to whatever stress, me resign
Sign it over, get back my spine
[Chorus]
Me trade you my hands, take back my mind
Give you the small things, me go design
You run the lines, me rewrite time
Me give up a little, get back a shrine
Me trade you my hands, take back my soul
You do the math, me feel whole
You count the kind, me change the role
Me give up control, gain full control
[Verse 2]
If me let go, will I really lose?
If me gain scope, that a better boost
Me say yeah all this, you say more room
Now my life big like a burst cocoon
But if me lean in, power come back
Take the routine, me run the track
We a tech team, can't turn back
Me drop one weight, leave full span
[Chorus]
Me trade you my hands, take back my mind
You do the small things, me go design
You run the lines, me rewrite time
Me give up a little, get back a shrine
Me trade you my hands, take back my soul
You do the math, me feel whole
You count the kind, me change the role
Me give up control, gain full control
[Outro]
Full control
Full control
